        "# US Co2 Emission Growth by Percentage\n",
        "\n",
        "## Overview\n",
        "Start with base data of global Co2 indexes. The raw data contains the following variables.\n",
        "* country\n",
        "* year\n",
        "* population\n",
        "* iso_code\n",
        "* gdp\n",
        "* cement_co2\n",
